{"tid":772700,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼城擬用「赫特」命名訓練場","createTime":"2018-08-09T03:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T08:17:27.000Z","uid":31314,"like":123,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"2dadefe6931dce844912010cc80772a52ef3051a","tid":772700,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T03:37:25.000Z","msg":"門將赫特日前正式離開曼城，以350萬鎊低價轉投般尼，但可能獲得意料之外的「餞行禮」。<br />\n<br />\n效力曼城長達12年的赫特（Joe Hart），有望獲得高格調的告別禮，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>球會打算把其中一個青訓球場命名為「赫特球場」，名留後世。</strong></span> 31歲前英格蘭一號門將赫特，曾為曼城上陣超過340場，贏過2次英超、2次聯賽盃和1次足總盃，但在哥迪奧拿入主後被棄用。 今年5月，耶耶托尼離開效力8年的曼城，獲得同等「禮待」，把青訓營16個球場之一改名為「耶耶托尼球場」，主席穆巴拉克表示：「赫特的貢獻不能低估，12年時間很長，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>多年一直是一號門將，也肯定是史上的傳奇人物，祝福他明天會更好，曼城永遠歡迎他。</strong></span>」"},{"pid":"116bdd45b0f9b044149ed1c916092f496f9fe9ac","tid":772700,"uid":87573,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"人情味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f6f9b3b4038aba0dbffe9c80d299ee3113ff68","tid":772700,"uid":19552,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:02:13.000Z","msg":"好過皇馬"},{"pid":"95f1078387d3c59dcd84ace3faa1c30abc75f56f","tid":772700,"uid":23734,"like":40,"dislike":3,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"2dadefe6931dce844912010cc80772a52ef3051a","tid":772700,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T03:37:25.000Z","msg":"門將赫特日前正式離開曼城，以350萬鎊低價轉投般尼，但可能獲得意料之外的「餞行禮」。<br />\n<br />\n效力曼城長達12年的赫特（Joe Hart），有望獲得高格調的告別禮，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>球會打算把其中一個青訓球場命名為「赫特球場」，名留後世。</strong></span> 31歲前英格蘭一號門將赫特，曾為曼城上陣超過340場，贏過2次英超、2次聯賽盃和1次足總盃，但在哥迪奧拿入主後被棄用。 今年5月，耶耶托尼離開效力8年的曼城，獲得同等「禮待」，把青訓營16個球場之一改名為「耶耶托尼球場」，主席穆巴拉克表示：「赫特的貢獻不能低估，12年時間很長，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>多年一直是一號門將，也肯定是史上的傳奇人物，祝福他明天會更好，曼城永遠歡迎他。</strong></span>」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:04:36.000Z","msg":"門面功夫啫<br />\n<br />\n不過係有啲球會連呢啲都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeece127a685fb123570be28f40e7f79d760e2ce","tid":772700,"uid":31314,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"24f6f9b3b4038aba0dbffe9c80d299ee3113ff68","tid":772700,"uid":19552,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:02:13.000Z","msg":"好過皇馬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:05:41.000Z","msg":"卡斯拿斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f0138be28a1b517a144cb07b1bc4275ad0945c","tid":772700,"uid":10089,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:07:10.000Z","msg":"曼城少有本土legend"},{"pid":"920a1cf5104b0076750e42271a685c472ac91ee2","tid":772700,"uid":555,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:09:19.000Z","msg":"獌迷仲關心過鏝迷<br />\n唔講仲以為佢地有份命名訓練場"},{"pid":"a431953cd7cdbe48335ff2553b1e84c95e1a58be","tid":772700,"uid":5549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:10:45.000Z","msg":"都值既，hart有段時間好勁"},{"pid":"9d3bc2aa7a9632cf63e61001be551968ae074d35","tid":772700,"uid":28435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:13:44.000Z","msg":"YNWA"},{"pid":"e732cd04d3bdaa0ba3429fa27b3ca9b852b7e6ed","tid":772700,"uid":4661,"like":156,"dislike":5,"score":151,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:14:30.000Z","msg":"香港一早改左<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/37/HK_TST_Hart_Avenue_1-9_EMPaST.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F3%2F37%2FHK_TST_Hart_Avenue_1-9_EMPaST.JPG&h=f3829a1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4e597c242474ad35e4550e225e74e00fead55d0","tid":772700,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T04:16:12.000Z","msg":"曼城咁好點解要撚狗咁撚佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a302b0b3be8e8b1afd9858f826869efb52eec02","tid":772700,"uid":31314,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e4e597c24